{"lastModified":1775224563749,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nHAPPY is a luxurious 55 ft. catamaran built by Lagoon. A model created by passionate designers for sea lovers searching for freedom. HAPPY features 4 cabins and accommodates 8 guests. A vessel with nothing left to chance, Lagoon has designed it in all its\nsmallest details. You can enjoy a gentle lifestyle on board of HAPPY, far from the constraints of daily life.","blueprint":{"name":"HAPPY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe2aad10-1a9e-11f0-9765-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe292670-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe288a30-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fdff3040-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe2a37e0-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fdeabde0-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe27edf0-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe29e9c0-1a9e-11f0-9765-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe270390-1a9e-11f0-9764-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fe2ad420-1a9e-11f0-9765-254365388a48/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7c3dee90-3564-11ef-8e27-d52d0bbcf4ce::assets::fdfebb10-1a9e-11f0-9